@JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5053

### List products (public) — paged JSON: items, totalCount, page, pageSize, totalPages
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=12&search=&sortBy=relevance
Accept: application/json

### Category names (filters)
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### Admin dashboard stats (Admin / Employee)
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Sales summary by month (Admin / Employee) — query: months=1..36, default 12
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/sales/summary?months=12
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin users — paged (Admin only)
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users?page=1&pageSize=10&search=
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin roles dropdown (Admin only)
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Patch user role / active (Admin only) — at least one of roleId, isActive
PATCH {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": true
}

### Register (JSON body: name, email, password, confirmPassword)
POST {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Test123!"
}

### Login
POST {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@joyeriamarr.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### My profile (any authenticated user)
@token = YOUR_JWT_HERE
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/account/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### My orders — paged (paste Bearer token from login response)
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/orders/my?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### All orders — Admin / Employee (paged)
GET {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/orders?page=1&pageSize=10&search=
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create order — Customer role only
POST {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Gift wrap please",
  "lines": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### Create custom-line order — Customer (no productId; price 0 until quoted)
POST {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Budget up to $800",
  "lines": [
    { "quantity": 1, "customDescription": "Yellow gold ring, emerald, size 7" }
  ]
}

### Update order status — Admin / Employee
PATCH {{JoyeriaBackend_HostAddress}}/api/orders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "In Progress"
}

###
